      <title>联邦党人协会主席告诉团体他正在寻找继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/federalist-society-head-tells-group-he-s-searching-for-successor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻社获得的一封电子邮件显示，美国颇具影响力的保守派法律组织联邦党人协会的长期负责人正准备卸任，并已开始寻找继任者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/federalist-society-head-tells-group-he-s-searching-for-successor</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 20:06:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>左翼政党在欧盟选举中赢得荷兰多数席位，威尔德斯遭遇挫折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/left-wins-most-dutch-seats-in-eu-election-in-setback-to-wilders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲议会选举中，左翼政党联盟赢得了荷兰最多席位，令吉尔特·威尔德斯刚刚组建的执政联盟以及整个欧洲大陆的保守民粹主义者遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/left-wins-most-dutch-seats-in-eu-election-in-setback-to-wilders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>税收收入不足迫使哥伦比亚实施国家支出冻结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/weak-tax-revenue-forces-colombia-to-impose-state-spending-freeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于税收收入不足，哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗的政府正在冻结国家机构和公共机构的预算。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/weak-tax-revenue-forces-colombia-to-impose-state-spending-freeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙承诺向乌克兰派遣战斗机并训练军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/macron-pledges-to-send-fighter-jets-and-train-troops-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，法国将向乌克兰派遣战斗机并训练数千名士兵，帮助该国击退俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/macron-pledges-to-send-fighter-jets-and-train-troops-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 19:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约立法者考虑在霍楚尔收费站撤销后提高营业税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ny-lawmakers-weigh-business-tax-hike-after-hochul-toll-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州立法者正在考虑提高纽约市企业的税收，以帮助填补因州长凯西·霍楚尔意外决定停止拥堵收费计划而造成的每年 10 亿美元的资金缺口，该计划原本可以为重要的交通基础设施改善提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ny-lawmakers-weigh-business-tax-hike-after-hochul-toll-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:44:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党计划周五召开关键会议，敲定英国大选提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/labour-plans-crunch-meeting-friday-to-finalize-uk-election-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党将于周五在一个秘密地点举行关键会议，敲定其选举宣言的最终细节，但其与工会之间可能会就工人权利承诺发生争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/labour-plans-crunch-meeting-friday-to-finalize-uk-election-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:28:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国内改革面临障碍，米莱取消 G7 峰会和马克龙访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-cancels-g-7-macron-visits-as-reforms-face-hurdles-at-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱取消了下周前往意大利参加七国集团峰会的计划，并放弃了与法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙原定的会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/milei-cancels-g-7-macron-visits-as-reforms-face-hurdles-at-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
