      <title>波兰召见白俄罗斯特使，就边境附近士兵被杀事件展开讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/poland-summons-belarus-envoy-over-soldier-s-murder-near-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰外交部召见了白俄罗斯驻华沙特使，就一名试图非法越境的移民刺伤一名士兵致其死亡一事展开讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/poland-summons-belarus-envoy-over-soldier-s-murder-near-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 18:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
